'''Harlan Ottekvar''' was to portray [[Lord/Legends|Lord]] [[Baltharog]] in the holofilm adaptation of the book ''[[Quest for Quasar]]'', in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]]. He was criticized by fans of the original work, particularly [[Groz Niclari|Groz "QuasarKing327" Niclari]]. Reasons included Ottekvar being too short to portray Baltharog (1.84 meters, and 1.86 meters in boots) and that he was too famous.

His other works included ''[[SuperKnight: The Awakening]]'' and ''[[Webb Tenger: PeaceBuster]]''.

